     2	
     3	Use the security policy for identity, permissions, and authorization checks.
     4	Use the checkout process for basket checkout tasks.
     5	Use the discount policy before applying or refusing basket discounts.
     6	Use the payment policies before recovering payment workflow failures.
     7	Use the returns policy before approving or finalizing customer refunds.
